headline: First Trust Expands Target Outcome® Lineup with Launch of DGOC, A 10% Buffer ETF that Seeks to Provide Positive Return Potential in Up, Flat, and Modestly Down Markets
summary: WHEATON, Ill., October 20, 2025--First Trust Advisors L.P. ("First Trust") a leading exchange-traded fund ("ETF") provider and asset manager, announced today that it has launched the FT Vest U.S. Buffer & Digital Return ETF – October (Cboe: DGOC) (the "fund").
